      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s looking for a new home! It\u2019s been super reliable and still runs like a charm. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-cared for, making it perfect for daily commutes or fun weekend road trips. You're going to love how smooth it handles\u2014come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
