    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six with its signature individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This example boasts a reinforced rear subframe\u2014a critical preventative measure\u2014and a recently overhauled double-VANOS system for optimal cam timing. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed manual transmission to a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry remains tight, providing the communicative steering and balanced turn-in these chassis are renowned for. A mechanically honest machine for the serious enthusiast.",
      "price": 31500.0,
