    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers the perfect balance of rugged capability and everyday comfort. The exterior retains its original deep luster, with only minor, expected road wear consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium upholstery is free of tears, and the dashboard remains crack-free with all tactile buttons and digital displays functioning exactly as they should. Mechanically, this car stands out with a comprehensive service log, including a recent major interval check, fresh fluids, and a set of high-quality tires with plenty of life remaining. It has been a smoke-free, pet-free environment throughout its ownership. Whether you're navigating city streets or heading off the beaten path, this car provides a confident, smooth ride that reflects its history of responsible stewardship.",
      "price": 36500.0,
