      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new-to-you ride? I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s still in wonderful shape! It\u2019s been well-loved and runs like a dream\u2014perfect for daily commutes or weekend adventures. You\u2019re going to love how smoothly it handles, and it looks great too. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
